(42, 10, 18, 58, 2, 14, 14, 'Satan as lightning fall from heaven', 'Connection of Satan''s Defeat', 'This connection highlights the theme of Satan''s fall and defeat. In Luke 10:18, Satan''s fall is depicted as a decisive event, while Hebrews 2:14 speaks of Jesus destroying the devil''s power through death.', 'theme', 0.43999999999999995, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
