(42, 10, 19, 41, 16, 18, 18, 'power to tread on serpents', 'Power Over Harmful Creatures', 'Both passages emphasize the power given to believers over dangerous creatures and harmful substances. They highlight the assurance that nothing shall hurt them when acting in faith.', 'theme', 1.0, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 10, 19, 44, 28, 5, 5, 'nothing shall by any means hurt you', 'Power Over Harmful Creatures', 'This connection highlights the theme of divine protection over harmful creatures. In Luke 10:19, the promise of power over ''serpents and scorpions'' parallels Paul''s experience in Acts 28:5, where he suffers no harm from a snake.', 'theme', 1.0, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 10, 19, 45, 16, 20, 20, 'power of the enemy', 'Power Over the Enemy', 'This connection highlights the theme of divine empowerment over evil forces. Both passages emphasize the authority given to believers to overcome Satan and his power.', 'theme', 1.0, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
